鄭秋玲 兼任副教授







































 鄭秋玲   兼任副教授
最高學歷 ：國立中興大學博士
專 長：昆蟲分類學
電話：(05)2717815傳真：(05)2717816
E-mail：clcheng@mail.ncyu.edu.tw

開設課程：無脊椎動物學、昆蟲分類學
 
(A)期刊論文
1.        Cheng, C.-L. and Yang, C.-T. 1991. A new species of Ecapelopterum of Taiwan (Homoptera: Issidae). Chinese J. Entomol. 11(3): 228-230.
2.        Cheng, C.-L. and Yang, C.-T. 1991. Nymphs of Issidae of Taiwan (I) (Homoptera). Chinese J. Entomol. 11(3): 232-241.
3.        Cheng, C.-L. and Yang, C.-T. 1991. Nymphs of Issidae of Taiwan (III) (Homoptera). Plant Prot. Bull 33(4): 323-333.
4.        Cheng, C.-L. and Yang, C.-T. 1991. Nymphs of Issidae of Taiwan (IV) (Homoptera). Plant Prot. Bull 33(4): 334-343.
5.      Cheng, C.-L. and Yang, C.-T. 1992. Nymphs of Issidae of Taiwan (II) (Homoptera). Taiwan Museum 45(1): 29-60.
